title: After Governor’s Win, DeSantis Grabs National Spotlight
description: The Florida governor’s victory was a result of his commanding campaign, relentless voter registration and turnout efforts, and Democrats’ utter collapse in the state.
dc:creator: Patricia Mazzei

media:content.media:credit: Scott McIntyre for The New York Times
media:content.media:description: With the national spotlight squarely on him, Gov. Ron DeSantis could for the first time experience intense scrutiny from the right — starting with former President Donald J. Trump.
